{"tid":747300,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"攝影台的愛情故事","createTime":"2018-07-18T09:13:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T05:23:11.000Z","uid":11779,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a6c8a0698870c3b7d496388aaa50036e93f7ea46","tid":747300,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T09:13:22.000Z","msg":"自從含撚貓千古後，咖哩味就茶飯不思，心中都是貓sir貓sir, 點解你要係貓sir呢 我要係咖哩味？簡直係天意弄人！<br />\n唉！ 平時係人面前扮敵對，但內心不知幾傾慕傻貓，為左掩飾對貓sir的愛 就日日用Canon屌鳩Sony，心中既又痛恨陳綺貞先生條撚奪去含sir朱脣嘅第一次，但他又無恥的硬了。<br />\n<br />\n最愛嘅人已經離開攝影台 佢已經冇勇氣就出post. 思前想後 佢出最後一個post自爆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就連不sir我都深受感動，平時唔會貼圖嘅 都忍唔住用罪大影返幅相紀念呢個可歌可泣的愛情故事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/171019_6f48aae5a4e910cc238e0f26cb69f6f3.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F171019_6f48aae5a4e910cc238e0f26cb69f6f3.jpeg&h=4428f9ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仆街黃蛙又死圖！"},{"pid":"d53bf1370ebbc02833087ac3f08cfb46e335947b","tid":747300,"uid":11779,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T09:50:27.000Z","msg":"不sir我貼圖都冇人理？有冇搞錯！"},{"pid":"bd8f3c3cb2c682088ad8f36623522b8862395b9f","tid":747300,"uid":163554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T14:08:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d617330e6b3789769131fb779810e5d92c0c8cb4","tid":747300,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bd8f3c3cb2c682088ad8f36623522b8862395b9f","tid":747300,"uid":163554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T14:08:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T14:28:28.000Z","msg":"成班仆街成日話我唔貼 到我貼時又扮睇唔到"},{"pid":"5dafd59020504559c4d6b9b29d3d6307ee6a2acc","tid":747300,"uid":148192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T00:20:02.000Z","msg":"一早話佢地有路，不過佢地之間仲有個第三者叫唔知咩藥稀，個第三者次次都護住咖哩去屌sony<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},